ยง 19-101. Laws repealed. 1. The following sections of the civil rights
law are hereby repealed:
 Section sixteen, as added by chapter one hundred fifty-seven of the
laws of nineteen hundred twenty-one;
 Section seventeen, as added by chapter eleven of the laws of nineteen
hundred thirty-five.
